    "summary": {
      "value": "Bind a previously unknown Arcanum, and improve dismiss effects."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Requirements: </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">you must have mastered the </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Arcanist </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Class.</span></p></blockquote><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You make contact with an unknown Arcanum and bind it to your soul. This Arcanum must be something you design together with the rest of the group; as long as you live, no one else in your world will be able to bind that Arcanum.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Once per scene while you are </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>merged </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">with an Arcanum, you may use an action and spend 2 Fabula Points to </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>trigger </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">that Arcanum's </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>dismiss </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">effect (if any) without dismissing them. Doing so </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>does not</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">trigger the </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>@UUID[Compendium.fabula-ultima-core-rulebook.skills.Item.hEj8s21iAOPhDtJN]{Arcane Circle}</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Skill (<strong>Core Rulebook</strong>, page </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>177</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">).</span> </p>",
